channel.title: The Worst Pop Singer I've Ever Heard
channel.description:
Well, I was forced to hear this song on the way home with my sister, and while listening I noticed how awful the singer was. So, I looked it up to share it with you. In my opinion, the chick has the most terrible voice, even with auto-tune. She can't sing worth shit and just talks normally with a rhythm. It's quite sad.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=edP0L6LQzZE&ob=av3n Kesha - Take It Off
~Lin
